race.description: Road To Magic Millions Book Now Hcp
race.comment: The babies kick us off. BOOMELLI (3) couldn't have been more impressive when saluting by four lengths at the Sunny Coast on debut and winning rider Thompson sticks in the saddle. Will have taken a stack of confidence from that dominant victory and looks very hard to hold out again. ITCHINTOGO (1) is facing the starter for the first time but looked handy winning a recent trial and is sure to be well-educated out of the Gollan barn. Respect any market confidence. LEAVES OF LORIEN (5) put in a better effort last time out and seems to be improving with racing. One for the multiples. MAGRITTE (4) next in line on the back of a debut placing here.
